node.text:
A special double length comic about Wilson and his fave new cushion! Swipe to the end to see a photo of the boy himself! 😼

Heya! I've got two spooky sweaters available to preorder right now! One is a brand new design called Skeleton House, and the other is a reprint of Pumpkin Patch - that last one is a timed preorder that ends THIS WEDNESDAY so get your order in now to make sure you get your size!

There's other spooky bits too! Go have a look and get spooky! It's never too early for spooky season! 💀🎃💀🎃💀

#comics #webcomic #instacomic #comicstrip #igcomic #sarahgraley #oursuperadventure #comic

This cat-themed throwback is from Our Super Adventure Volume 2! 

Heya! We've just launched pre-orders for a brand new spooky sweater and a whole bunch of new enamel pins! There's also a week-long pre-order for Pumpkin Patch sweaters - if you missed out before, here's your chance!

Also - I still have a few portrait commission slots available! All details are on the link in my profile!

node.text:
🎃🎃🎃 Spooky season approaches! 🎃🎃🎃

I'm launching a whole bunch of new spooky pins and a brand new spooky sweater on Wednesday! I'm so excited to share the new designs with you all!

I'm also opening up a week long pre-order for pumpkin patch sweaters on Wednesday too - we had a bunch of people get in touch asking us to restock it so make sure you set an alarm if you want one!

Lastly, my portrait commissions will open up again on Wednesday! I'll be taking on a limited amount of commissions for September so get in early if you want one! I've had so much fun drawing everyone and their pets!

#comics #webcomic #igcomics #comicstrip #instacomic #wholesome #spooky #halloween #sarahgraley #oursuperadventure
